## Dimension: Completeness

**Definition**: The degree to which the narrative summary addresses all major claims, agreements, disagreements, and uncertainties from the synthesis without omission.

**Why This Matters**: A narrative summary must be comprehensive. Omitting major themes or conflicting viewpoints from the consolidated synthesis undermines the utility of the Delphi process.

